wiki.summary: "Jelly Pop" is a song recorded by the trainees of BOYS PLANET. It is the first track on the single FINAL TOP9 BATTLE, released on April 21, 2023. Performed during the show's final episode, the members included Lee Hoetaek (CUBE Entertainment), Zhang Hao (Yuehua Entertainment), Jay (FM Entertainment), Na Kamden (FNC Entertainment), Park Hanbin (WAKEONE Entertainment), Seok Matthew (MNH Entertainment), Yoo Seungeon (Yuehua Entertainment), Kum Junhyeon (Redstart ENM) and Park Gunwook (Jellyfish Entertainment). Read more on Last.fm.
wiki.content: "Jelly Pop" is a song recorded by the trainees of BOYS PLANET. It is the first track on the single FINAL TOP9 BATTLE, released on April 21, 2023. Performed during the show's final episode, the members included Lee Hoetaek (CUBE Entertainment), Zhang Hao (Yuehua Entertainment), Jay (FM Entertainment), Na Kamden (FNC Entertainment), Park Hanbin (WAKEONE Entertainment), Seok Matthew (MNH Entertainment), Yoo Seungeon (Yuehua Entertainment), Kum Junhyeon (Redstart ENM) and Park Gunwook (Jellyfish Entertainment). The track was written by Kim Anna and composed & arranged by imsuho, Naasim and Dr. Han, with Chris Wahle and Ryan Lawrie credited as co-composers. Read more on Last.fm.
